Program options:
  -h [ --help ]         show help
  -c [ --client ]       start client chat
  -s [ --server ]       start server chat

Client options:
  --ip arg                   address of server
  -p [ --port ] arg (=10000) server port
  -n [ --name ] arg          user name

Server options:
  -t [ --threads ] arg (=1)  number of threads
  -p [ --port ] arg (=10000) listening port

